node.text:
The new era of @GasMonkeyGarage is here and one of YOU will be taking home a car from my private collection! 

How can you enter to win? Head over to GasMonkeyGarage.com and snag some GMG gear. Every $1 you spend, gets you one entry to win one of my cars. 

We’ll also be giving away weekly cash prizes! What are you waiting for? GYSOT NOW at GasMonkeyGarage.com!

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings

node.text:
I’m ecstatic to announce that I’ll be the celebrity guest judge for this years virtual Fat Guys Car Show! If you’re in the Thunderbay, Canada area, you can enter your pride and joy into this virtual car show and win one of many cash prizes, with best-show winning $1,000!

I just wonder, why was I chose for the Fat Guys Car Show? 🤔

If you want to get in on the fun, register for the 10th Annual @fatguysautoparts car show today at FatGuysCarShow.com

node.text:
Over the weekend we picked up a 1978 F-250 and well let's just say that towing it back didn't exactly go as planned! GMG needs a quick flip and that means you can snag this truck for a great deal. $30k OBO, the best offer in 24 hours gets it! 

If you're interested in it, send us an email at Info@GasMonkeyGarage.com or check it out at Inventory.GasMonkeyGarage.com (link in bio)

Also, yes I know that I said 1979 multiple times when its a 1978, cut me a little bit of slack 😅

#GasMonkeyGarage #GasMonkey #RichardRawlings #FastNLoud #AmericanMuscle  #Truck #Truck #Carporn #ClassicCars #ClassicTrucks #AmericanMuscle #FordTrucks #Ford
